        <Parent_String>filmmaking forms and presentations [300375199], image-making processes and techniques [300053159], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any film presentation with an aspect ratio of 1.85, flat. Most wide-screen processes are anamorphic but some such as Panavision 70 and Todd-AO employ wide gauge film or overlapping multiple projectors such as with Cinerama.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052809/Cook, A History of Narrative Film (1993)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Filmvertoning met een beeldverhouding van 1:1,85 'flat'. De meeste breedbeeldprocedés zijn anamorfotisch, maar bijvoorbeeld Panavision 70 en Todd-AO maken gebruik van een brede filmmaat of meerdere overlappende projectoren, zoals bij Cinerama.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>以1.85的影像寬高比放映的電影。多數寬螢幕的製作程序是橫向擠壓，但有些寬螢幕製作則使用寬規格的電影膠捲，例如潘那維辛體70(Panavision 70)和陶德寬螢幕 (Todd-AO)，或者是如新藝拉瑪體(Cinerama)採用數台放映機重疊放映製成。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
